[[File:Alfex_Cargo_Stacks.png|thumb|right|250px|The Alfex Cargo Stacks]]
'''Alfex Cargo Stacks''' was a cargo complex on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal]]. Its business was sorting cargo bound for the same destination into individual shipments, which were then sent to transports to be delivered. Alfex was also a front for [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]]. Black Sun's local leaders based themselves out of specially outfitted rooms hidden in Alfex's cargo containers, where they coordinated criminal operations on the planet, including [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]].<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

